                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850511-39-off221 t17850511-39-cd222"></join> last, one live cock, price 2 s. and four live hens, price 8 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850511-39-victim463" type="victimName">
